Events.Text:
<i>Lex seemed nice,░ we clicked well enough when they got over the club a little,░ a little rough around the edges and certainly not angling for anything romantic tonight.░ But a good friend,░ for now,░ that I was happy to have bumped into.░
If I'd stayed clinging to Coby on the dance floor,░ I certainly would have missed the opportunity.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: Success
Events.Title: [Editor Comment]

Events.Text: <i>Lex's car wasn't too far away,░ it was a pretty nice model,░ not a fancy sports car but it seemed well-loved:░ it certainly put my own car to shame with the empty water bottles and receipts cluttered around the front seats.░ The car was well-maintained despite that they'd mentioned owning it for years.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>There was a slight woody smell of warm tobacco, maybe even cigars,░ that made me think of my grandparents' house.░
We sat side-by-side in the front,░ rolling our chairs back a little to stretch out,░ Lex, in the driver's seat, played disk jockey from a media player hooked into the sound system.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Lex didn't seem like they'd beefed up the sound system much, at first,░ though considering the age of the car the USB connected hardware and the clarity of the guitars that came through the speakers proved otherwise,░ definitely better than the tinny-sounding ones that struggled to play along in my own car.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Lex walked me through some of their favorite songs,░ pointing out their favorite parts, but saving an in-depth discussion until a second listen through.░ They really knew their stuff and had details on some of the more obscure bands in the alternative rock genre.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>We couldn't sit in the car all night without running down Lex's battery,░ the night wasn't quite cool enough not to need the AC running in the confined space either way.░ Lex started up the engine and we drove around the strip a little with the windows down and the tunes turned up.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>Lex seemed to brighten up away from the club scene and driving stopped them from checking their phone every ten minutes to see if their absent friends had responded.░ We simply hung out together,░ concentrated on the music and the ambient sights and sounds of the city at night.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text: <i>The husky didn't really have any destination in mind:░ in fact, they said they just enjoyed driving around in general.░ Despite what I thought with the sporty car model and the torn pants,░ Lex was a pretty safe driver,░ almost cautious,░ and took each turn with impressive precision on the push and pull of the wheel,░ never crossing their hands or letting go the way my dad would terrify me with.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>After warming the car up a little, we found ourselves at Burger Wolf for a late night snack and milkshakes to beat the heat.░ Nothing too fancy,░ and nothing that hinted at romance.░
For better or worse,░ on that last point,░ I felt at ease around Lex and if they took a while to warm up to people I considered this a good start.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>I hadn't really explored the genre of music in too much depth and,░ though it might never be my favorite,░ Lex was a passionate guide to the genre as we went on our little driving adventure.░
We ended up talking away a good chunk of the night by the time Lex dropped me back off at the club.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
<i>I was familiar with a handful of the bands Lex showed off on our little driving adventure,░ though they had a couple of cross-genre surprises and certainly knew how to pick a good song.░
Our back-and-forth about the genre whiled away a good chunk of the night by the time Lex dropped me back off at the club.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Hey,░ I had fun tonight, %playername%.░
We should do something like this again some time.
Events.Title: Lex

Events.Text:
That'd be pretty awesome.░
I had fun too!░ You'll definitely have to send some of those songs over when you get home.░
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Of course!░
Hey, take my number too, right?░ Gimme a call or text or something when you're free.░ I can usually make time if I'm all caught up with work.
Events.Title: Lex

Events.Text: I definitely will.░ Drive safe Lex, I'll text you later.
Events.Title: %playername%

Events.Text:
Always do.░
See ya, dude.
Events.Title: Lex

Events.Text: <i>We shared a friendly handshake that was somewhere between a gang sign and a high five as they thanked me for the night and waded through the crowd to freedom.
Events.Title: %playername%
